This directory contains an encapsulation
of the Open Dynamics Engine (ODE) simulation library
for Matlab (Mac OS X and Linux).

To run a simulation of a 3D hopping robot,
just run hopper.m

hopperInit: Initialize robot body and geometry
hopperReset(a0): Reset robot position with starting angle a0
hopperStep(dt): Run simulation steps for dt time
hopperState: Returns structure containing state of robot
hopperControl1(hip1, hip2, vankle): Simple PD hip control, set ankle vel
hopperPlot: Simple plotting routine for robot
